body_html:
When I try to install libtool:

brew install libtool
Warning: libtool-2.4.6 already installed, it's just not linked

When I try to install libtoolize:

brew install libtoolize
Error: No available formula for libtoolize 
==> Searching formulae...
==> Searching taps...
==> You haven't updated Homebrew in a while.
A formula for libtoolize might have been added recently.
Run `brew update` to get the latest Homebrew updates!
MacBook-Air:tensorflow appcenter$ brew update

I have libtool but not libtoolize :
/usr/local/Cellar/libtool/2.4.6/share/aclocal/libtool.m4

```
brew install libtool

```

**When I try to install libtoolize:**

```
brew install libtoolize
Error: No available formula for libtoolize 
==> Searching formulae...
==> Searching taps...
==> You haven't updated Homebrew in a while.
A formula for libtoolize might have been added recently.
Run `brew update` to get the latest Homebrew updates!
MacBook-Air:tensorflow appcenter$ brew update

```
